      "text": "Living in the Faroe Islands honestly looks like choosing peace and dramatic weather over noise and traffic forever. Tiny villages, giant cliffs, and endless ocean views somehow make modern city life feel emotionally exhausted. Honestly, even the sheep there probably have lower stress levels than most office workers.",
